Rating: 3
Comfort food is a great discription!! Chops that aren't too thick are important to the sucess of the "crust". If the chops need to sautee too long to cook though, bread crumbs will fall off. Also, the traditional 3 step breading process works well [ 1) dredge in seasoned flour, 2) dip in beaten egg, 3) dredge in seasoned bread crumbs].

